# 2. ようこそワンダーステージへ！

Tsukasa: Well, well. It's pretty busy even on a normal weekday. Phoenix Wonderland sure is popular.
Tsukasa: Which makes it a perfect place for my debut as a star!
Tsukasa: My story will begin today by first passing the audition with ease.
Tsukasa: Glowing reviews of my performances will keep the audience seats filled at every show, which will always end with a standing ovation, as my fandom continues to grow!
Tsukasa: Thus the curtain will rise on the legend of Tsukasa Tenma, epic superstar!
Tsukasa: Hehehe... Ha ha ha ha ha! Perfection!
Staff: Excuse me... Are you here for the job interview? You're in the wrong place, buddy.
Tsukasa: What... And where is the right place?
Staff: The interviews are being held in that building over there. You'll have to go around that way, so it's a bit of a walk...
Tsukasa: This can't be happening! I'll be late! I must make it somehow!
Tsukasa: Pardon me for my rudeness unbefitting of a star! Please accept my late thanks for your kind advice! Well then, I must be on my way!
Staff: What's up with that kid...
Tsukasa: *Huff*... *Huff*... I made it... My legend nearly ended before it even had a chance to begin!
Interviewer: We will now begin interviewing the next group of applicants. Please come this way.
Tsukasa: Coming! Hehe, now I can finally show off my talents!
Interviewer: We'll start from the right side. Please begin with a brief introduction.
Applicant: Hello. I decided to apply to work at this park because...
Tsukasa: (First impressions are everything at job interviews. Go big or go home! I must outshine everyone else right from the very beginning!)
Interviewer: Next, please...
Tsukasa: My first name is written with the character for ruling, and second with the characters for pegasus. I am Tsukasa Tenma, the soaring pegasus born to rule the showbiz world!
Interviewer: What the?!
Tsukasa: Allow me to take my first steps to stardom on one of your stages, and I shall repay you with a plethora of incredible shows the crowds will fall in love with!
???: Did someone say “incredible shows”?
Tsukasa: I am not merely a star, I am a supernova! I am the miracle-bringer! And now, I am at your service!
Interviewer: Er... Thank you. Next, please...
Tsukasa: (Hahahahaha! My introduction left them speechless! I'm guaranteed to pass this interview with flying colors!)
???: Hehehe☆ Perfect!
Tsukasa: Naturally, I passed the interview! Success is the only option for the star-to-be that I am!
Tsukasa: Next, I will surely be selected for the main role in a major performance. Tickets will sell out at the mere mention of my name!
Tsukasa: My fame will only keep snowballing, resulting in an avalanche of offers from the top theater troupes around the country!
Tsukasa: Fast forward a few years and I'll be a dazzling star standing on the grandest stages of the world! Ha ha ha ha!
???: Wow. Some weirdo's just loudly talking to himself...
???: Spring tends to bring out people like that... I better hurry home to play some games.
???: Oh ho? That was an unusual fellow. He went in the direction of the theme park...
???: Hmm. Perhaps I should head over there too♪
Tsukasa: New hires were to wait by the main gate... So around here.
Mascot: *poke*
Tsukasa: Whoa! Wh-What do you want?!
Mascot: My apologies for startling you. I'm an employee of the park. Am I correct in assuming you are Tsukasa Tenma, starting today?
Tsukasa: Gulp... That deep voice really doesn't match the mascot image... Hold on, he may be a park mascot, but he's my senior here!
Tsukasa: Yes, that's me! It's a pleasure to work with you!
Tsukasa: Do you know which stage I've been assigned to?
Mascot: It is over that way. You can't see it from here. Please follow me.
Tsukasa: Okay!
Tsukasa: (That must be the newly built Neo Phoenix Rollercoaster? And that would be the renovated Neo Phoenix Castle!)
Tsukasa: (They've built quite a few new attractions over the last few years. Everywhere you look, it's brand spanking new. But, well, it IS one of the best theme parks in the country!)
Tsukasa: (Hehe... I can't wait to see my new stage! If it's also been recently renovated, it will be dazzlingly gorgeous for sure!)
Tsukasa: Um, are you sure this is the right way? We've been walking for a while...
Mascot: We are almost there.
Tsukasa: But... This place is almost empty, if you don't count the overgrown shrubbery...
Tsukasa: Huh? The path continues further?
Tsukasa: You're seriously going to lead us through that jungle? Oh, it looks like the path opens up into a clearing?
Tsukasa: Is this a...stage? It looks in serious need of repairs. What does it say on the signboard here...
Tsukasa: “Wonder Stage”?
???: Haaaaaaaaaaaaah!
Tsukasa: Whoa! What on earth was that? Something just dropped out of the sky!
???: Welcome to the Wonder Stage, a place filled with lots of smiles☆
???: All together, now! One, two, wonderhoy☆
Tsukasa: Huh?
???: Wonderhoy!
Tsukasa: Can you stop now?
???: Wonder...
Tsukasa: Okay, I'll do it! Wonderhoy, wonderhoy, ahoy! Are you satisfied now? Who are you anyway? Where did you drop from?
???: From up there!
Tsukasa: Where? Are you out of your mind?! That's, like, two stories high!
???: Yup! I wanted to give you a surprise welcome, Tsukasa!
Tsukasa: Well, it was a surprise, that's for certain. But how do you know my name?!
???: Of course I know your name! I invited you here, Tsukasa!
Tsukasa: What?
Emu: I'm Emu Otori! Welcome to the fantastic Wonder Stage, a place filled with lots of smiles!
Emu: Let's put on some incredible shows together, Tsukasa!
Tsukasa: Huh...? W-Whaaaaaat?
Tsukasa: What the heck is going on?!
